;Перезагружаем телефон 
;Startup animation not needed, choices 
;To the choosed directory (def. /usb/other/gfx) save your graphics, 
;in XXXX.PNG (def.) / GIF format - depends on choice, 
;where XXXX is the HEX number of the replaced image. 
